<p>
Please send your images to <span class="missing">quizzes@muddled-times.com</span>. The best one will be voted for after the next issue and all images will be added to the <a href="personae.fod">Persona Pictures</a> gallery.<p><br clear=all><div align="center"><span class="missing">Mail the author</span><br><br></div><div align="right">... <a href="issue.fod_IssueId_27">click here</a> to return to the front page.</div>
